185
00:25:28,386 --> 00:25:29,444
What is your father's name?
-I don't have one.

186
00:25:29,588 --> 00:25:31,222
Mother?
-I don't have one.

187
00:25:31,222 --> 00:25:32,416
Are you an orphan?
-No.

188
00:25:33,124 --> 00:25:35,388
How were you born then?
- I wasn't born, I was made.

189
00:25:36,528 --> 00:25:42,267
