this world.

217
00:28:17,455 --> 00:28:20,424
His eyes are not just to see, but also to show.

218
00:28:26,464 --> 00:28:28,261
We can speak to him virtually.

219
00:28:28,566 --> 00:28:30,056
With these type of robots..

220
00:28:30,268 --> 00:28:33,260
